## CSS

### Token-first — no magic numbers
All design decisions live in `:root` custom properties. Reference tokens everywhere else:

```css
/* ✅ Define once */
:root {
    --bg:        #f0f4f8;
    --surface:   #ffffff;
    --border:    #e2e8f0;
    --text:      #1e293b;
    --text-dim:  #64748b;
    --accent:    #0ea5e9;
    --danger:    #ef4444;
    --radius:    10px;
    --shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, .08);
    --shadow:    0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, .10);
}

/* ❌ Never inline a raw colour not in tokens */
.card { background: #f0f4f8; }

/* ✅ */
.card { background: var(--bg); }
```

### Dynamic values via custom properties
Pass runtime values through CSS custom properties on the element, not through inline `style` objects:

```tsx
// ✅ — declarative, CSS can reference it transitively
<div style={{ '--mode-color': color } as React.CSSProperties}>

// ❌ — bakes the value into the DOM attribute; can't be referenced in CSS
<div style={{ color: color }}>
```

### Naming — BEM with a ware prefix
`.{ware-slug}` for the root, `__element`, `--modifier`:
```css
.kanban { }              /* root */
.kanban__header { }      /* element */
.kanban__board { }       /* element */
.column--drag-over { }   /* modifier */
```

Never use ID selectors (`#id`) in component CSS. Avoid deep chains (`.a .b .c`) — one level of nesting max.

### Focus visible — required
Every file that styles interactive elements must include visible `:focus-visible` styles:

```css
button:focus-visible,
input:focus-visible,
[tabindex]:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
    outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

Never `outline: none` or `outline: 0` without a custom replacement.

### Transitions — specific properties only
```css
/* ❌ Forces the browser to check every property */
transition: all 0.2s ease;

/* ✅ */
transition: background 0.12s ease, color 0.12s ease;
```

### Reduced motion
Any animation or transition that serves a visual-only purpose must be dampened:

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    *, *::before, *::after {
        animation-duration:        0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1      !important;
        transition-duration:       0.01ms !important;
    }
}
```

### Box model reset — first thing in every CSS file
```css
*, *::before, *::after {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    margin:     0;
    padding:    0;
}
```

### Units
| Use case | Unit |
|---|---|
| Font sizes | `rem` (relative to `:root`) |
| Component-relative spacing | `em` |
| Borders, fine-tuned spacing | `px` |
| Full-height layouts | `100dvh` / `100svh` |
| Avoid | `vw`/`vh` (use `dv*` variants) |

### Layout
- `gap` between flex/grid children — not margin hacks.
- `z-index` always has a comment: `z-index: 100; /* above sticky header */`
- No `!important` except inside resets.

